<author>ạ̉sbyr ạljldẗ, ạ̉sbyr ạljldẗ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̉nạ fy ạlmṣlwb ạ̉ḥyạ whw fy ạ̉ʿmạq dẖạty
 mlʾ qlby mlʾ rwḥy mlʾ fkry wḥyạty
 whw ʿwny wạlrjạʾ
 ḥynạ knt wḥydaⁿạ fy ẓlạl ạlmwt ạ̉mḍy
 wṭryqy kạn rḥbaⁿạ ạ̹nmạ llmwt yfḍy
 ṣạr ʿwny wạlrjạʾ
 ạ̉jrty kạnt hlạky ạ̉jrẗ ạlkẖạṭỷ ạlạ̉tẖmy
 whw mn ḥl wtẖạqy wạrtqy̱ by llnʿym
 tẖm ạ̉ʿṭạny ạlrjạʾ
 lm ạ̉ʿd ạ̉kẖsẖy̱ ʿdwy ạ̹n tmạdy̱ bạlsẖrwr
 fslạm ạlrb ḥṣny wklạm ạlrb nwry
 whw ly lḥn ạlrjạʾ</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉nạ fy ạlmṣlwb</title>
</song>